### ðŸ§© Day 1 â€“ [1407. Top Travellers](https://leetcode.com/problems/top-travellers/)
**Difficulty:** Easy  

```sql

SELECT 
    u.name AS name,
    COALESCE(SUM(r.distance), 0) AS travelled_distance
FROM Users u
LEFT JOIN Rides r
    ON u.id = r.user_id
GROUP BY u.id
ORDER BY travelled_distance DESC, name ASC;
